channel.title: TASAHM-Scape V1 MAP DEVOLUTiON BASE 100% SKILLS AWESOME SeRVER!
channel.description:
Reason I am releasing: Well Devo 2.6 just came out and it looked really sexy so I want to start working on that. Client: Any thing you like. Deob: 317-377
Features: All the nice Devolution Shizzle(2.4) Plus some Monstascape Stuff I think. The shops are a bit bare because I never got round to them. The Allstar Skilling Area, Pkbox and Reapage home. (Access to these areas can be turned on and off at the convenience of a command) This server can be made into a serious economy server or a pking one just by typing ::pkingmode A start for NvN (Never finished) REAL ALLSTAR GSMINI!!!!!!! Full Woodcutting + mining + Smithing (With differing Exp rates depending on mode) Screen and Minimap go black whenever a new area is loaded. Its just a really nice base. Btw I did not just copy and paste the Allstar + Reapage areas I rewrote all the codes so they are the shortest possible. Everything has a description. When you are about to enter a pking zone (For the first time this log in) You are frozen and warned about the approaching danger Im sorry that im not allowed to release Cj's client. Yes there will be a V2 based off of Devo 2.6 (This one will be more economy based) The void for Crafting is in there I just never did the itemOnItem Code
Features of Woodcutting: Accurate Tree Timers Etc Trees go into Stumps Trees Come back from stumps Type of Axe and Skill level make a difference you get logs and trees run out of logs.
Features of Mining: Rocks go Black Skill level and Pick affect Timing Accurate Timers etc.
Features in Pkingmode: Allstar Skills Much Faster exp rates Gsmini
Ummm thats about it really. There would be more but Devo 2.6 looked so appealing.
PICTURES!!!!!:(Ill let you admire Cjs client)
[center] BLACK SCREEN WHILE SHIZZ LOADS (Stays for about 1 second (Mostly) Really hard to get pic) [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/BlackScreen.jpg[/img] Cant move before entrance to pk zones [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/Frozen.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/Gsmini.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/Home.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/PkingBox.jpg[/img] Can't go through some portals when pkingmode is deactivated(Just in case someone does get in the shit inside is deactivated too) [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/Pkingmode.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i368.photobucket.com/albums/oo123/tatemo/Tasahm%20scape/Skills.jpg[/img][/center]
Credits: Silent Cj for his love and support XD(Plus the current shops were made by him) Killamess for tonnes(This guy should get lots of love) Acf for being part of the project(even though he cant code XD) Me for being so awesome Reapage + Allstar for being the best sources ever released (Just badly coded)
Here is server Download link: http://www.mediafire.com/?mojntzke4il
